Package com.vincestyling.asqliteplus.statement

Package of statement which included all the Statements producer.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Alias This class used to producing an ALIAS clause which temporary renaming the object(could be table||column||function) as a given name in a particular SQL statement.
ClauseWrapper A base class for implementations which served a clause.
CreateStatement A statement producer that use to producing INSERT command of SQL language.
DeleteStatement A statement producer that use to producing DELETE command of SQL language.
Exists This class used to producing an EXISTS operator clause which used to tests whether a sub-query fetches at least one row.
Function This class provides many static utility methods for wrapping those useful built-in functions of SQLite during constructing SQL statement.
NotExists Appending the NOT EXISTS operator clause by a sub-query.
Parenthesize This class used to parenthesizing the specified statement.
QueryStatement A statement producer that use to producing SELECT command of SQL language.
Scoping This class used to producing a clause which included column name and table scope.
Statement A base class for constructing SQL statement.
UnescapeString This class used to wrapping a String which you don't want to be auto quoting.
UpdateStatement A statement producer that use to producing UPDATE command of SQL language.
